     "text": [
      "--- Transaction 1: Shopping Mall ---\n",
      "Processing your transaction for card number 1234567890123456\n",
      "Card Holder name is Shahzaib Baig\n",
      "Payment recieved successfully 4500\n",
      "Payment is processed by card. The holder name is Shahzaib Baig\n",
      "--- Transaction 2: Online QR Scanner ---\n",
      "Initiating UPI payment request via ID: shahzaib@upi...\n",
      "Waiting for secure MPIN authentication...\n",
      "Rs. 120 successfully transferred via UPI gateway.\n",
